data.title: About Hakan Karlsson
data.meta_description: Born and raised in Sweden but live in Quito, Ecuador, since 2005, I love to take pictures of nature, animals and daily life of people. Though I like to get better to work with pictures in Photoshop I still like when my pictures stay as original as possible.
